description:
Alia Janine and her natural 34FF monster boobage is back. We love hot Milf's all spread out and vulnerable, don't you?
The game is simple, we whip you until you say "tickle", then we tickle you till you say "whip". We do this without mercy, without remorse, with total focus on destroying her rational thought. She simply becomes an animal, fighting for breath, fighting for a break, fighting to endure a situation that is no-win. Deciding to take one evil over another evil, it is the cruelest of games, but one that is really fun to watch..
title: Alia Janine
